ynergism', 'The risk of hepatic injury should be considered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/289246/', '', 'Ritodrine, Bremelanotide, Bromocriptine, Cabergoline, Alprostadil, Ubidecarenone, Ivabradine, Adenosine, Regadenoson, Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Amivantamab, Atezolizumab, Pembrolizumab, More', 1767369485);
